---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About me">
    <section>
        <h2>About Me</h2>
        <p>
            Hello! I'm a passionate Fullstack JavaScript Developer with a strong
            background in building dynamic and responsive web applications. My
            expertise spans across both frontend and backend technologies,
            enabling me to create seamless and efficient user experiences.
        </p>

        <h3>Frontend Development</h3>
        <p>
            I specialize in crafting intuitive and engaging interfaces using
            modern frameworks like React, Angular, and Vue.js. My focus is on
            writing clean, modular, and maintainable code while ensuring the
            best performance and user experience.
        </p>

        <h3>Backend Development</h3>
        <p>
            On the server side, I am proficient with Node.js and Express,
            developing robust and scalable APIs. My experience includes working
            with databases such as MongoDB, MySQL, and PostgreSQL, as well as
            integrating various third-party services and APIs.
        </p>

        <h3>Fullstack Projects</h3>
        <p>
            Having worked on numerous projects, I have a comprehensive
            understanding of the full software development lifecycle. From
            ideation and design to deployment and maintenance, I strive to
            deliver high-quality solutions that meet business needs and exceed
            user expectations.
        </p>

        <h3>Technologies & Tools</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>
                <strong>Frontend:</strong> HTML, CSS, JavaScript, TypeScript, React,
                Angular, Vue.js
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Backend:</strong> Node.js, Express, GraphQL, RESTful APIs
            </li>
            <li><strong>Databases:</strong> MongoDB, MySQL, PostgreSQL</li>
            <li>
                <strong>DevOps:</strong> Docker, Kubernetes, CI/CD pipelines, AWS,
                Azure
            </li>
            <li><strong>Others:</strong> Git, Webpack, Babel, Jest, Cypress</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Passion & Growth</h3>
        <p>
            I am constantly learning and staying up-to-date with the latest
            trends and technologies in web development. I enjoy taking on new
            challenges and collaborating with others to create innovative
            solutions. My goal is to make the web a better place, one line of
            code at a time.
        </p>

        <h3>Let's Connect</h3>
        <p>
            Feel free to reach out to discuss potential projects,
            collaborations, or just to chat about tech and development. I'm
            always open to new opportunities and connections.
        </p>
    </section>
</Layout>

